Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:21:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}姐姐 姐姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别 别扯我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小圆 好难受啊
